MY ACNE JOURNEY + HOW I GOT RID OF IT NATURALLY!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
(Had to divide the video into two parts because it wasn't getting uploaded as one 😩) Part 1 is my acne story and Part 2 is how I got rid of it! 
I had it for about 2 years and could only dream of having clear skin. Even now, my skin isn't clear but if you've gotten rid of the acne, that's 80% of your job done, because atleast you have even texture! 
If you want to know what my skin looked like before, head over to my 'Acne advice' highlight. Shoutout to my sister @dreamingatmydesk who made me a skincare routine and made sure I stuck to itttt (while slightly threatening me)
Hope you like the video and do share it with anyone who's going through the same thing! Much love ❤️❤️
